Description: Replay Guitar Exchange proudly presents this American-made Fender American Professional Stratocaster from the year 2016, in a 3-Color Sunburst finish with a 3-ply mint green pickguard. This guitar was masterfully crafted from an alder solidbody with a smooth and easily playable maple neck that hosts a rosewood fingerboard. Three V-Mod single-coil Strat pickups power this monstrous guitar, producing an exceptionally natural and versatile tone that can be shaped by the five-way blade switch. This guitar is in Very Good condition, with no issues to specifically point out aside from the estimated 90% of fret life remaining. A modern benchmark for classic and irreplaceable guitar tones, this American Professional Stratocaster is a huge step into the world of fantastic guitars. As always, feel free to contact our store for more details, or with any questions. Weight: 7 lbs. 10 oz.
